# Generated stats snapshot (scripts/collect_stats.py)
stats.json

# Retired ai4privacy corpus derivative (Sprint 9 — license non-OSS, see
# docs/process/LICENSE_AUDIT.md). Historical commits still contain this
# file; we just prevent accidental re-add.
tests/fixtures/corpora/ai4privacy_sample.json

# Meta-classifier training JSONL is regenerated locally via
# `python -m tests.benchmarks.meta_classifier.build_training_data`
# and no longer committed (retired with ai4privacy drop, Sprint 9).
tests/benchmarks/meta_classifier/training_data.jsonl

# ML models (too large for git, exported via `python -m data_classifier.export_onnx`)
# The Phase 2 meta-classifier artifacts are small (~8 KB combined) and
# committed per decision D5 — everything else in this directory is
# ignored by default.
data_classifier/models/*
!data_classifier/models/__init__.py
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v1.pkl
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v1.metadata.json
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v1.eval.json
# Sprint 11 Phase 2/3: v2 meta-classifier artifact (46-feature schema,
# 44 kept features after ALWAYS_DROP_REDUNDANT, feature_schema_version=2).
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v2.pkl
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v2.metadata.json
# Sprint 11 Phase 7: v3 meta-classifier artifact (47-feature schema,
# 45 kept features after ALWAYS_DROP_REDUNDANT; includes
# heuristic_dictionary_word_ratio at index 46, feature_schema_version=3).
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v3.pkl
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v3.metadata.json
# Sprint 12 Item #1 + Item #2: v5 meta-classifier artifact (49-feature
# schema, 47 kept features after ALWAYS_DROP_REDUNDANT; adds
# validator_rejected_credential_ratio at index 47 and
# has_dictionary_name_match_ratio at index 48, feature_schema_version=5).
# Schema v4 was transient and never deployed — Phase 2 added index 47
# but the artifact was never trained before Phase 3 appended index 48.
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v5.pkl
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v5.metadata.json
# Research candidate artifacts from parallel experiments (meta-classifier queue).
# Same size class as v1; see docs/experiments/meta_classifier/queue.md file-ownership.
# Allows candidate suffixes like meta_classifier_v1_q3.pkl, meta_classifier_v5_e12.pkl.
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v*_*.pkl
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v*_*.metadata.json
# Keep the gliner_onnx/ placeholder directory (populated by download_models CLI
# at container build time) so package_data globs have a target, but ignore the
# actual model weights.
!data_classifier/models/gliner_onnx/
data_classifier/models/gliner_onnx/*
!data_classifier/models/gliner_onnx/.gitkeep
!data_classifier/models/gliner_onnx/README.md
models/gliner_onnx/
